Booster seat: 12 EUR per day. Maximum 60 EUR. Includes 20% tax; On request

Child toddler seat: 12 EUR per day. Maximum 60 EUR. Includes 20% tax; On request

Infant child seat: 12 EUR per day. Maximum 60 EUR. Includes 20% tax; On request

